    "context": "\"You dismissed \" + _event.m.Fired + \", a veteran of the company\""
  },
  {
    "key": "ae31efc9bb7ce0a89c17317e6d702b0584f6bd73fe7518a2ae9d3464a76b1d5b",
    "original": "Along the way...",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Title = \"Along the way...\""
  },
  {
    "key": "7db40749d1ebcbc790af2eb088aeda7f903521c7230f34fec7ef7e976941ad79",
    "original": "They'll get over it.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"They'll get over it.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "283fcd89ebeaa19f0cd44145198ce2e9bbecfdb58e31a53e4c628ffac8d8fe41",
    "original": "You dismissed ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"You dismissed \" + _event.m.Fired + \", a veteran of the company\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8f058031751a5a986625656d46f9160e832670fb9dc2ef97427e59ef821faaa1",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_64.png[/img]It was a tough decision, but you had to cut %dismissed% loose. However, it appears you should have consulted the rest of the men first for none of them are happy with your choice. The mercenary had been in the company long enough to make friends, and even those who weren't close to him still felt as though his place on the battlefield ensured their own safety.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_64.png[/img]It was a tough decision, but you had to cut %dismissed% loose. However, it appears you should have consulted the rest of the men first for none of them are happy with your choice. The mercenary had been in the company long enough to make friends, and even those who weren't close to him still felt as though his place on the battlefield ensured their own safety.\""
  }
]